ws if one assumes that the yield point\nis the critical point of an underlying out-of-equilibrium phase transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2011 03:22:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2013 13:55:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-24"}
