sus can be solved in anonymous systems with only partial synchrony\n(and a majority of correct processes).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2011 14:09:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2011 10:45:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 27 Nov 2011 13:32:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-11-29"}
